  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We have launched! Thank you to everyone that has supported me! We're far from done! Below i have put together a small road map with upcoming content! Please keep a look out for them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090630/extras/5d9c99c95f1b19f6760c5644fa16661e.avif?t=1727283852\" width=616 height=106 /></span>Puzzle Dungeon!! Earthmage Erin is a puzzle game where you change the direction of gravity to guide key cubes into their designated holes in dynamic dungeons. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress, you'll encounter new mechanics that add complexity and challenge, ensuring a continuously engaging experience!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090630/extras/21cc7cace0e4e66a74225ac8f32d0e11.poster.avif?t=1727283852\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090630/extras/21cc7cace0e4e66a74225ac8f32d0e11.webm?t=1727283852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090630/extras/21cc7cace0e4e66a74225ac8f32d0e11.mp4?t=1727283852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090630/extras/f46f8b84428555ebb50ae5f71e8e460c.avif?t=1727283852\" width=616 height=106 /></span>While you can complete the game without them, bonus objectives add extra layers of complexity to solved puzzles. Achieving these bonuses enhances Erin's farm, showcasing your progress and accomplishments. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additionally, hidden keys within certain levels unlock even more challenges to conquer!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090630/extras/1d35afb768a7276d92f344fb4a89cfc3.poster.avif?t=1727283852\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090630/extras/1d35afb768a7276d92f344fb4a89cfc3.webm?t=1727283852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090630/extras/1d35afb768a7276d92f344fb4a89cfc3.mp4?t=1727283852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090630/extras/cb4014b41904d31cc8c7b40f9c517c51.avif?t=1727283852\" width=616 height=106 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We have launched! Thank you to everyone that has supported me! We're far from done! Below i have put together a small road map with upcoming content! Please keep a look out for them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090630/extras/5d9c99c95f1b19f6760c5644fa16661e.avif?t=1727283852\" width=616 height=106 /></span>Puzzle Dungeon!! Earthmage Erin is a puzzle game where you change the direction of gravity to guide key cubes into their designated holes in dynamic dungeons. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress, you'll encounter new mechanics that add complexity and challenge, ensuring a continuously engaging experience!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090630/extras/21cc7cace0e4e66a74225ac8f32d0e11.poster.avif?t=1727283852\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090630/extras/21cc7cace0e4e66a74225ac8f32d0e11.webm?t=1727283852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090630/extras/21cc7cace0e4e66a74225ac8f32d0e11.mp4?t=1727283852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090630/extras/f46f8b84428555ebb50ae5f71e8e460c.avif?t=1727283852\" width=616 height=106 /></span>While you can complete the game without them, bonus objectives add extra layers of complexity to solved puzzles. Achieving these bonuses enhances Erin's farm, showcasing your progress and accomplishments. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additionally, hidden keys within certain levels unlock even more challenges to conquer!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090630/extras/1d35afb768a7276d92f344fb4a89cfc3.poster.avif?t=1727283852\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090630/extras/1d35afb768a7276d92f344fb4a89cfc3.webm?t=1727283852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090630/extras/1d35afb768a7276d92f344fb4a89cfc3.mp4?t=1727283852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090630/extras/cb4014b41904d31cc8c7b40f9c517c51.avif?t=1727283852\" width=616 height=106 /></span></p>",
